## 3. Honor-Based Commercial Support

If you or your company generate **more than USD 100,000 per year** in gross revenue using this Software or a derivative of it, you are **strongly expected** to:

- Contact the author (Discord: Watermann) Or GMail: musicenignebusiness@gmail.com
- Provide a **yearly sponsorship of your choice**

There is **no fixed price**.
This system is based entirely on **honor, fairness, and mutual respect**.

The intention is to support:
- development
- maintenance
- and the open community around the project

